{"tid":2156245,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"地方的創作者需要支持","createTime":"2020-08-14T10:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T10:34:53.000Z","uid":241026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"76a7c81c1662df63289977958b6e1b79c34c32f3","tid":2156245,"uid":241026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"近日，大家對蘋果、告急黃店等嘅支持十分踴躍，香港人其實有非常強大嘅資本能力去支持唔同嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n而其實有一樣嘢都好需要大家去關注，就係香港嘅本土文化。之前果籽做左個關於庫爾德人嘅系列，顯示左人地點解可以為左自己嘅民族、國族去付出代價，正正就係因為人地對於自己嘅地方有住一個強烈嘅歸屬感，守護自己與別不同嘅文化緊係理所當然。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9LPxj0ID4vM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9LPxj0ID4vM&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcRF66oQwccw1TbdUPfwT%2FAY%3D&h=130cfd83\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9LPxj0ID4vM</a><br />\n<br />\n好多時我地成日話香港音樂好似已經日落西山，但其實只不過係我地無去好好咁發掘非主流嘅創作，盡自己能力去支持一啲仍然繼續努力嘅音樂人。<br />\n<br />\n十月三十一日，將會有一個由TTN舉辦嘅線上音樂節。主辦單位都透露過搞online show其實成本仲可能仲甘過搞一個live show，而事實成個活動真係好撚貴。<br />\n<br />\n因此，雖然呢個show係大家可以係當日㩒條link就睇到，但希望大家都可以經濟上支持下，而越早買飛就越好，因為佢地有個安排就係會俾啲大金主去出席佢地四隊嘅錄影現場(可行嘅話)。<br />\n<br />\n同埋記住要些牙俾更多人知，我地自己文化就靠我地自己去守護同發揚光大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我自己都係喺第一次online show先真正接觸indie，發覺香港真係有好多好嘢，我真係好撚鍾意香港呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳情就去翻TTN嘅page度睇啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Thistownneeds/posts/3348875971838737\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FThistownneeds%2Fposts%2F3348875971838737&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcRF66oQwccw1TbdUPfwT%2FAY%3D&h=bc520c4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Thistownneeds/posts/3348875971838737</a>"},{"pid":"c6ff87d602bac4fb2eda77bbef44cfd6d0c70148","tid":2156245,"uid":241026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t4oPdFg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft4oPdFg.jpg&h=ec6f5647&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a812e6596ba476b755c3904b8c10eb46a9973127","tid":2156245,"uid":241026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:15:43.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3709d0dab98a01dd359fd12d31593d7c57a81389","tid":2156245,"uid":241026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:16:16.000Z","msg":"熱門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583e66de0dac50a410617466d777ad90bd2673da","tid":2156245,"uid":241026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:33:12.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa1bf5e13d1f1f3efe21d5f14e0dd954ca5dc77","tid":2156245,"uid":218315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T10:34:53.000Z","msg":"幫推"}]}